{"tid":726093,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"終於明白點解揸車咁怕廢老亂鳩過馬路","createTime":"2018-07-02T06:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T09:04:42.000Z","uid":149212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f15a2001be46b898a02d61b442ee0ff2c2a4623","tid":726093,"uid":149212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"學緊車一個月都無, 早排上堂師傅教上三波叫我試下, 咁我跟住做俾油加速啦<br />\n前面死車中間有個廢老突個頭出嚟望路面情況, 我以為佢會等我過咗先<br />\n點知佢見住個學神開緊埋嚟, 仲拖住身後兩個細路施施然行去對面, 仆街俾佢嚇一嚇好在剎得切架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n距離再近少少都出事, 唔怪得新聞咁多廢老被車撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd909acad633a0bb2b65660484a0e78f23dc50e","tid":726093,"uid":72735,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"&quot;以為人地會xxx&quot;<br />\n九成車禍都係咁引起<br />\n揸車一定要小心<br />\n唔肯定就收慢先"},{"pid":"24bd1ef69a3c6ed02c254d5bafd870b3345ea286","tid":726093,"uid":85223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:22:38.000Z","msg":"意外就係意料之外<br />\n你幾小心都可能出事<br />\n不過你唔爭個幾秒就幾大都停左先唔好搏<br />\n佢之後唔行一回事<br />\n你學神再撞真係以後都唔洗揸車"},{"pid":"e113b2a3846dffc9accb034dc0a90bc64e13aff3","tid":726093,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"好多廢老唔撚望車架<br />\n咪撚同佢地癲"},{"pid":"c18a1513bb496f0b98c464a43e72ab6c85b31ed1","tid":726093,"uid":84116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"佢肯凸個頭出黎望下先已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff38f5b92c8b66254d76fad2a0aea7d2ed2013db","tid":726093,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:30:27.000Z","msg":"話就話佢死<br />\n但你都要坐監 佢條命賤過地底泥 唔好同佢博"},{"pid":"2163c534246b880cca71bb455e813ef1d979bd1f","tid":726093,"uid":1067,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:33:48.000Z","msg":"見到三寶，放定隻腳喺個brake度一定無錯"},{"pid":"3d6131a8ba8ff60ca0f9211d644ae30ecd40b8db","tid":726093,"uid":33566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"揸得車就要預左所有情況<br />\n你見到條爛坦廢老果下就已經要收油放定腳係brake<br />\n你唔會知條死仆街會唔會衝出黎<br />\n呢個係安全意識"},{"pid":"e82ae10640e589a56183019422e8d4012a7f0aac","tid":726093,"uid":149212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:04:42.000Z","msg":"學神有一半集中力放咗轉波度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次經一事長一智"}]}